{"tid":1825140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日女乘客搭香港快運航空「遭強制驗孕」","createTime":"2020-01-15T04:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T07:29:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3f88c9a1dedf3bcd78e5565236db814c28e9fffb","tid":1825140,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BAk2SrslN0wQUN9KYgArHw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/mirrormedia.mg/a78ecb6aa0d3413f6cf889f4a8eb001f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FBAk2SrslN0wQUN9KYgArHw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2Fa78ecb6aa0d3413f6cf889f4a8eb001f&h=d182270f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一位25歲的日本籍女乘客搭乘香港快運航空（Hong Kong Express Airways），欲飛往美屬塞班島（Saipan）探親，儘管事前她已經在問卷上註記未懷孕，仍被強制要求驗孕，接受測試後證明該名女乘客並未懷孕，但整個過程讓她感到「非常羞恥和沮喪」，引起議論。<br />\n<br />\n根據《福斯新聞》引述《華爾街日報》報導，香港快運航空為此爭議事件道歉，並解釋從2019年2月起就對所有飛往塞班島的班機採取這項措施，以確保不違反美國《移民法》。香港快運航空對所有受到影響的人道歉，表明將中止這個做法。<br />\n<br />\n美國向來吸引大批外國產婦前往待產生子，以便讓小孩一出生就有美國籍，成為美國公民。2018年，美屬塞班島所在的美國北馬里亞納群島（Northern Mariana Islands），由遊客生下的孩子比當地居民生的還多！這裡之所以特別受到中國人歡迎，是因為它不需要簽證。目前美國並未禁止孕婦進入領土，但如果被發現疑似是想在美國待產生子的旅客，美國移民局官員有權拒絕其入境。<br />\n<br />\n擔任塞班島州長辦公室祕書的包蒂斯塔（Kevin Bautista）指出，不只是移民問題，產婦和胎兒的健康狀況也令人憂心，懷孕後期很可能出狀況，但這樣的待產旅行，往往沒有留下任何醫療紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n塞班島一直努力抑制遊客的出生率，但同時又希望保有對中國遊客有效的豁免計畫，因為中國遊客被視為對島上經濟至關重要。為此，去年塞班島向中央提出立法限制生育旅遊（birth tourism），同年10月3日，美國國土安全部門、美國海關和邊境保護局通過將免簽證旅遊時間從45天縮減為14天，並建議遊客持有遊覽群島各島嶼的來回票。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A5%B3%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%BF%AB%E9%81%8B%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA-%E9%81%AD%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E9%A9%97%E5%AD%95-%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E9%99%B8%E5%AE%A2%E6%83%B9%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%8D-105742005.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2590%25AD%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%2581%258B%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E9%25A9%2597%25E5%25AD%2595-%25E7%25AB%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2583%25B9%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25A6%258D-105742005.html&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=1d07e66e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A5%B3%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%BF%AB%E9%81%8B%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA-%E9%81%AD%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E9%A9%97%E5%AD%95-%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E9%99%B8%E5%AE%A2%E6%83%B9%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%8D-105742005.html</a>"},{"pid":"a9d4193db74b853bee039a3ed33222e6fa5092a2","tid":1825140,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:23:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【緊急】好多<span style=\"color: red;\">白人左翼</span>抹黑<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港人</span>！！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1824339/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1824339/page/1</a></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"eb7d18c35516ba759c674dc1de00166acbdf5803","tid":1825140,"uid":34854,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:25:10.000Z","msg":"以為要比人插入驗孕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccc50b8d496f28946802c245b97bfca4e74f1d3","tid":1825140,"uid":9315,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"支那人又陀衰家"},{"pid":"f659ff79adf717d1e35cdb58d703aedb814fedb3","tid":1825140,"uid":42340,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb7d18c35516ba759c674dc1de00166acbdf5803","tid":1825140,"uid":34854,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:25:10.000Z","msg":"以為要比人插入驗孕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"以為要比人中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\